io.gearpump.streaming.dsl.plan

Class GroupByOp<IN,GROUP>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.gearpump.streaming.dsl.plan.GroupByOp<IN,GROUP>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Op, java.io.Serializable, scala.Equals, scala.Product

    public class GroupByOp<IN,GROUP>
extends java.lang.Object
implements Op, scala.Product, scala.Serializable
    This represents an operation with groupBy followed by window aggregation.

    It can only be chained with WindowTransformOp to be executed in GroupByTask. However, it's possible a window function has no following aggregations. In that case, we manually tail a WindowOp with TransformOp of DummyRunner to create a WindowTransformOp.
